A simple tomato timer.

Features:

* 25 minute work timer
* 5 minute minimal break timer
* Minimum break timer automatically starts after tomato ends
* Track tomatoes completed and tomatoes popped for the session
* Set iChat status for tomato / tomato break
* Dock icon badge displays remaining tomato time
* It's tomato shaped!


Credits:
Sounds were taken from the sweet Minutes.wdgt dashboard widget.

Tomato image was found on the internet.
